                     <interp inst="t17820410-71-person867" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was capitally convicted this sessions with Rawlins and Batster.</p>
               <p>Tried by the Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron EYRE.</p>
